<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.2.1">
<l>kampa mākaṭa laṭaittilaṅ kaikkumaṉ katirmuṭi yavaipattum</l>
<l>ampi ṉālaṟut taracavaṉ tampikka  ḷittava ṉuṟaikōyil</l>
<l>cempa lānirai ceṇpakam mātavi cūtakam vāḻaikaḷcūḻ</l>
<l>vampu lāmkamu kōṅkiya nāṅkūr vaṇpuru ṭōttamamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple where dwells the one who, having dammed the great crashing sea</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] having cut down with arrows</l>
<l>The ten rayed crowns of Lanka’s ruler,</l>
<l rend="indent">gave [all] to the king’s younger brother,</l>
<l>Is Vaṉpuruṭōttamam in Nānkūr where areca [trees] rise high</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] fragrance waft,</l>
<l>Encircled by rows of fine jackfruit, magnolia, mādhavi [creepers],</l>
<l rend="indent">mangos, and bananas.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
